{"tid":2517051,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「娛樂圈大戰」2大女星互爆醜聞，知名女星：正一臭雞！","createTime":"2021-05-05T05:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T05:43:01.000Z","uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"be961394c42defd478463ce418278258a150d12e","tid":2517051,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:31:39.000Z","msg":"早前麥貝夷大爆翟威廉「性伴侶多得驚人」，後來更牽連了好朋友裕美，暗示對方是第三者，結果引來性格一向直率的裕美開口反擊。裕美近日再度回應，她直言覺得麥貝夷有精神問題，與她相處有困難，為人自私。<br />\n<br />\n裕美近日再度回應麥貝夷事件，決定將真相公開。她表示2019年曾介紹林作好友Edmond Luk給麥貝夷認識，兩人拍拖至上年尾才分開。對於麥貝夷與翟威廉的關係，裕美表示女方曾透露與William只是朋友，所以肯定兩人沒有拍拖，但暗示她與翟威廉確實有私下約會過夜。<br />\n<br />\n而裕美也出言力撐翟威廉，因他誠實講出自己單身7年有性伴侶，發生羅生門後，裕美有與翟威廉聯絡，<span class=\"red\">兩人都認為麥貝夷的精神有問題。 </span>"},{"pid":"234ab52482efd4b5e680aec4a8e66119f9c0e050","tid":2517051,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:31:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"042630e05707c2629c8a26fa3a5d921a1f63cbdf","tid":2517051,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5170ab6f8fe36f08483bcf1785e01be9253f0c","tid":2517051,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:32:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2fc9c9d580eafd753f0d7c3a3fcf9964611b78","tid":2517051,"uid":188310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:32:37.000Z","msg":"愈亂愈好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b54c9068970a7f6350efb21e9f2bf59656629fe1","tid":2517051,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bd2fc9c9d580eafd